Naked pictures of Celebrity Big Brother contestant Jessica Cunningham have been unearthed - with someone offering the saucy snaps to the highest bidder. 
The raunchy photos show Jessica, who also appeared on the last series of The Apprentice, nude save for a wig covering her modesty on a night out. 
The pictures were taken several years ago, but friends believe Jessica will be extremely embarrassed if they ever see the light of day. 
“Jessica will be mortified,” a source told The Sun . “She enjoys a night out but she’s trying to carve out a career as a businesswoman and TV personality and is aware any bad publicity could ruin that. Read More Jessica, who's now in Celebrity Big Brother, is said to be mortified by the pictures (Photo: Channel 5) Jessica in action on The Apprentice (Photo: BBC) Jessica's family were upset she used to work as a stripper 
“She also has three children and doesn’t want them to be embarrassed.” 
Jessica, 29, sparked controversy on The Apprentice when she admitted she used to work as a £1000-per-day stripper , and the revelation upset her family. 
"I feel terrible, I'm their little girl. My mum is talking about seeing a therapist and my dad feels like he failed as a father,” she told the Sun on Sunday last month. 
"They worked so hard for me and are quite prudish so it’s hard for them to take. They’re embarrassed. Read More Jessica said she felt terrible about the stripping revelation (Photo: BBC) Jessica getting a massage from Calum Best (Photo: Rex Features) 
"Getting naked in front of strangers could make you feel insecure at times but for the most part I treated it as a laugh and got on with it," she added. 
"My first lap dance was such a blur. I know I was a bit too enthusiastic and goofy as hell. Early on I fell over a few times, which was embarrassing.” Like us on Facebook
